WEBVTT

00:01.801 --> 00:05.669
<i>Theorizing that one could time travel
within his own lifetime,</i>

00:05.739 --> 00:08.674
<i>Dr. Sam Beckett stepped
into the Quantum Leap accelerator...</i>

00:08.742 --> 00:10.733
<i>and vanished.</i>

00:15.348 --> 00:17.942
<i>He awoke to find himself
trapped in the past,</i>

00:18.018 --> 00:21.545
<i>facing mirror images
that were not his own...</i>

00:21.621 --> 00:26.854
<i>and driven by an unknown force
to change history for the better.</i>

00:26.926 --> 00:32.192
<i>His only guide on this journey is Al,
an observer from his own time,</i>

00:32.265 --> 00:36.634
<i>who appears in the form of a hologram
that only Sam can see and hear.</i>

00:36.703 --> 00:40.867
<i>And so, Dr. Beckett finds himself
leaping from life to life,</i>

00:40.940 --> 00:43.875
<i>striving to put right
what once went wrong...</i>

00:43.943 --> 00:47.071
<i>and hoping each time
that his next leap...</i>

00:47.147 --> 00:49.138
<i>will be the leap home.</i>

00:55.121 --> 01:00.286
<i>As one of the county's most celebrated
and dramatic murder trials was set to begin.</i>

01:00.360 --> 01:03.727
<i>1958.</i>

01:03.797 --> 01:07.233
<i>How long are you gonna
keep us tied up?</i>

01:07.300 --> 01:12.465
<i>What do you want? As convicted
murderer Leon Stiles escaped.</i>

01:12.539 --> 01:14.837
<i>I, uh-
Details remain sketchy at this time.</i>

01:14.908 --> 01:17.900
I don't want anything.

01:21.214 --> 01:23.409
Mommy, look, it's him!

01:23.483 --> 01:28.682
These are thought to be
the most recent photos of Stiles.

01:28.755 --> 01:32.156
Stiles escaped custody
in a daring daylight shootout.

01:32.225 --> 01:35.854
Stiles, described by authorities
as an illiterate drifter,

01:35.929 --> 01:38.159
was recently arrested
in connection with the murders...

01:38.231 --> 01:40.699
of at least eight women
in three states.

01:40.767 --> 01:45.295
At this moment, he is the central focus
in a county-wide manhunt.

01:48.842 --> 01:50.776
Oh, boy.

01:52.000 --> 01:58.074
Advertise your product or brand here
